## Phase 4: File Writing

### Objective

Parse Opus output and write CLAUDE.md and project-context/SKILL.md files.

### Process

```javascript
// 1. Parse Opus output by section markers
const opusOutput = synthesis.response;
const [claudeMdContent, projectContextContent] = parseOpusOutput(opusOutput);

// 2. Write files directly (no template substitution needed)
fs.writeFileSync('.claude/CLAUDE.md', claudeMdContent);
fs.writeFileSync(
  '.claude/skills/project-context/SKILL.md',
  projectContextContent
);
```

### Parsing Logic

```javascript
function parseOpusOutput(output) {
  const sections = output.split('---');

  // Extract CLAUDE.md content (between "# CLAUDE.md Content" and first "---")
  const claudeSection = sections[0];
  const claudeContent = claudeSection
    .replace(/^#\s*CLAUDE\.md Content\s*\n/, '')
    .trim();

  // Extract project-context content (after "# project-context/SKILL.md Content")
  const contextSection = sections[1];
  const contextContent = contextSection
    .replace(/^#\s*project-context\/SKILL\.md Content\s*\n/, '')
    .trim();

  return [claudeContent, contextContent];
}
```

