## Phase 5: Deterministic Resource Copying

### Objective

Copy skills, generate agents, and copy commands based on RULES ONLY.

### Execution

```bash
# Run the Phase 5 script
# Note: The framework path should point to where ai-agentic-framework is installed
bash .claude/skills/initialize-project/scripts/run-phase5.sh \
  $(pwd) \
  /Users/ignaciobarreto/itIsHere/projects/ai-agentic-framework
```

This script will:

1. Detect the stack using `stack-detection.js`
2. Select and copy skills using `skill-selection.js`
3. Generate and write agents using `agent-generation.js`
4. Copy commands
5. Generate index files
6. Display stack summary

### Stack Detection (Rules + Fallback)

```javascript
// 1. Use rules for known technologies
const rules = require('./config/stack-detection-rules.json');

// 2. Fallback to Phase 1 findings for unknown technologies
// This ensures ANY technology can be detected
const stack = detectStack(projectPath) || synthesis.tech_stack.languages;
```

### Skill Copying (Unchanged - This Is Solid)

```javascript
const skillsToCopy = new Set(SKILL_MAPPING.always);

for (const language of stack.languages) {
  const langSkills = SKILL_MAPPING.by_language[language] || [];
  langSkills.forEach(s => skillsToCopy.add(s));
}
// ... continue for frameworks, testing, etc.
```

