## Error Handling

| Phase | Error               | Recovery                              |
| ----- | ------------------- | ------------------------------------- |
| 1     | Agent timeout       | Retry with 2x timeout (max 3 retries) |
| 1     | Invalid JSON        | Retry with stricter schema prompt     |
| 2     | User doesn't answer | Use first option as default           |
| 3     | Opus invalid JSON   | Retry with explicit schema validation |
| 4     | Template error      | Log missing vars, use empty string    |
| 5     | Copy fails          | Log error, continue with remaining    |

---

## Idempotency

- **CLAUDE.md**: Always overwrite (backup as `.claude/CLAUDE.md.backup`)
- **project-context/SKILL.md**: Always overwrite
- **Skills**: Skip if exists
- **Agents**: Always overwrite
- **Commands**: Skip if exists
- **INDEX.md**: Always regenerate

---

## Testing Determinism

```bash
#!/bin/bash
# Run twice with identical answers
/initialize-project /path/to/project
cp -r /path/to/project/.claude /tmp/run1
rm -rf /path/to/project/.claude
/initialize-project /path/to/project
diff -r /tmp/run1 /path/to/project/.claude
# Should show no differences (except timestamps)
```

---

## Evolution History

| Aspect              | V1                   | V2.1                   | V3.0 (Current)                     |
| ------------------- | -------------------- | ---------------------- | ---------------------------------- |
| **Questions**       | Always 4 fixed       | 0 to N based on gaps   | Deep research first, then 0 to N   |
| **Gap Resolution**  | None                 | Agent ambiguities only | Exhaustive code + doc research     |
| **CLAUDE.md**       | 600+ lines, verbose  | 300+ lines             | 100-150 lines (quick ref only)     |
| **project-context** | Mixed with CLAUDE.md | Mixed with CLAUDE.md   | 250-400 lines (deep knowledge)     |
| **Duplication**     | High                 | High                   | Zero (complementary files)         |
| **Output Format**   | JSON with templates  | JSON with templates    | Text with section markers          |
| **Determinism**     | Same outputs         | Same outputs           | Same **process**, variable outputs |
| **Stack Support**   | Common only          | Any technology         | Any technology                     |
| **Philosophy**      | Rigid structure      | Freeform markdown      | WHERE/WHAT vs HOW/WHY split        |

